book-text-piratecode = [bold]Each[/bold] maggot, calling himself a realll pirate, [bold]must[/bold] follow pirate code. Each dumb ass, that [bold]breakes[/bold] it must be punished by the decision of the team. Each pirate crew [bold]must[/bold] choose a captain in the start of their journey. 
        1. Each pirate shall be proud of his title. 
        2. The only pirate's morals is the pirate code. 
        3. The only pirate's home is the ship.
        4. The only pirate's family is his crew. 
        5. The only pirate's goal is for the crew to get rich. 
        6. Pirate shall be ready to risk for the success of the fellows. 
        7. Pirate is forbidden to kill the innocents from the space ship. 
        8. Pirate is permitted to make a hole in the heads of his true enemies: the heads of the enemy ship, and their guards. 
        9. Pirate is forbidden to leave his teammate in trouble 
        10. Pirate must server his captain. 

 